law.text:
The plan to implement the pilot program shall:
Provide a useful educational medium for students in the pilot program;
Be capable of being implemented at a reasonable cost;
Encourage and develop students' familiarity with computer technology and train teachers to integrate such technology into their curriculum;
Add to the increased performance of the students participating in the program; and
Provide performance indicators that illustrate how teachers' familiarity with technology and teaching resources within the pilot program have increased.
